{"id":103,"parent_id":4,"book_id":4,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":103,"title":"D&C 99","subtitle":"","short_title":"D&C","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Section 99"],[".studyIntro",["i","Revelation given through Joseph Smith the Prophet to John Murdock, August 29, 1832, at Hiram, Ohio. For over a year, John Murdock had been preaching the gospel while his children—motherless after the death of his wife, Julia Clapp, in April 1831—resided with other families in Ohio."]],[".studySummary",["i",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.1-8"},"1–8"],", John Murdock is called to proclaim the gospel, and those who receive him receive the Lord and will obtain mercy."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.1","order":"06.05.099.12542"},["b","1"],"Behold, thus saith the Lord unto my servant John Murdock—thou art",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"called"],"to go into the eastern countries from house to house, from village to village, and from city to city, to proclaim mine everlasting gospel unto the inhabitants thereof, in the midst of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"persecution"],"and wickedness."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.2","order":"06.05.099.12543"},["b","2"],"And who",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"receiveth"],"you receiveth me; and you shall have power to declare my word in the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"demonstration"],"of my Holy Spirit."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.3","order":"06.05.099.12544"},["b","3"],"And who receiveth you",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"as"],"a little child, receiveth my",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"kingdom"],"; and blessed are they, for they shall obtain",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_3c"},"mercy"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.4","order":"06.05.099.12545"},["b","4"],"And whoso rejecteth you shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"rejected"],"of my Father and his house; and you shall cleanse your",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"feet"],"in the secret places by the way for a testimony against them."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.5","order":"06.05.099.12546"},["b","5"],"And behold, and lo, I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"come"],"quickly to",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"judgment"],", to convince all of their ungodly deeds which they have committed against me, as it is written of me in the volume of the book."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.6","order":"06.05.099.12547"},["b","6"],"And now, verily I say unto you, that it is not expedient that you should go until your children are",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"provided"],"for, and sent up kindly unto the bishop of Zion."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.7","order":"06.05.099.12548"},["b","7"],"And after a few years, if thou desirest of me, thou mayest go up also unto the goodly land, to possess thine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"inheritance"],";"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.8","order":"06.05.099.12549"},["b","8"],"Otherwise thou shalt continue proclaiming my gospel",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"until"],"thou be taken. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.1a","order":"06.05.099.12550"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/10.1.1-20"},"Luke 10:1 (1–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.1b","order":"06.05.099.12552"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/persecution"},"TG Persecution"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.2a","order":"06.05.099.12554"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.40.40-42"},"Matt. 10:40 (40–42)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.2b","order":"06.05.099.12556"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.4"},"1 Cor. 2:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.3a","order":"06.05.099.12558"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/18.4.1-14"},"Matt. 18:4 (1–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.3b","order":"06.05.099.12560"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/kingdom-of-god-in-heaven"},"TG Kingdom of God, in Heaven"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/kingdom-of-god-on-earth"},"Kingdom of God, on Earth"],"."],["div",{"id":"3c","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.3c","order":"06.05.099.12562"},["b","3c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mercy"},"TG Mercy"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.4a","order":"06.05.099.12564"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/12.49.44-49"},"John 12:49 (44–49)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.4b","order":"06.05.099.12566"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/75.20.19-22"},"D&C 75:20 (19–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.5a","order":"06.05.099.12568"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.12"},"D&C 1:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.5b","order":"06.05.099.12570"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/jude/1.15.14-15"},"Jude 1:15 (14–15)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-judge"},"TG Jesus Christ, Judge"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.6a","order":"06.05.099.12572"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/75.24.24-26"},"D&C 75:24 (24–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.7a","order":"06.05.099.12574"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/85.7.1-3,7,9"},"D&C 85:7 (1–3, 7, 9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.18.1,6,18"},"101:18 (1, 6, 18)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/99.8a","order":"06.05.099.12576"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.29"},"Matt. 19:29"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/self-sacrifice"},"TG Self-Sacrifice"],"."]]}
